{"tid":2517610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"New Xi Land總理宣布結婚","createTime":"2021-05-05T12:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T13:01:39.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"187bd3dcde75589d4aad48b34db16b79a605a039","tid":2517610,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:06:47.000Z","msg":"女兒已兩歲大 紐西蘭總理阿爾登預計今夏完婚<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5435872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F5435872&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=1844e354\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5435872</a><br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭媒體今天報導，總理阿爾登（Jacinda Ardern）計劃在今年夏季結婚，但未透露日期。阿爾登在2019年復活節假期間與伴侶蓋佛德訂婚，兩人育有一個兩歲女兒。<br />\n<br />\n「紐西蘭先驅報」（New Zealand Herald）報導，阿爾登（Jacinda Ardern）告訴紐西蘭海岸廣播電台（Coast Radio），40歲的她和44歲的未婚夫蓋佛德（Clarke Gayford）「終於敲定了」婚期。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述阿爾登的話說：「這並不代表我們已知會過任何人，所以我想我們或許應該發出一些邀請。」<br />\n<br />\n媒體引述她的話報導，兩人預計在今夏成婚，但可能不會按傳統儀式舉行婚禮，因為阿爾登說，她「覺得自己有點老了，不適合舉行婚前單身派對」。南半球的夏季為12月至2月。<br />\n<br />\n阿爾登2017年走馬上任，以37歲之齡成為紐西蘭1856年來最年輕總理，也是少數在任內懷孕的民選領袖之一。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭去年10月舉行國會選舉，阿爾登因防疫成績亮眼備受肯定，她領導的工黨贏得壓倒性勝利，支持率創下半世紀以來最高。"},{"pid":"dbfe7e0c219325272a61f3047cfb3cfd85db2427","tid":2517610,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343085926668439553.jpeg/22k_lbtPASBRITebo9O3VUmBslrveBRv19b3WdfW91k?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343085926668439553.jpeg%2F22k_lbtPASBRITebo9O3VUmBslrveBRv19b3WdfW91k%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=d33f65e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e3a7ec05e961ad837eedef220a2f7678227d258","tid":2517610,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbfe7e0c219325272a61f3047cfb3cfd85db2427","tid":2517610,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343085926668439553.jpeg/22k_lbtPASBRITebo9O3VUmBslrveBRv19b3WdfW91k?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343085926668439553.jpeg%2F22k_lbtPASBRITebo9O3VUmBslrveBRv19b3WdfW91k%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=d33f65e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:08:37.000Z","msg":"可能請你做伴郎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b433d14e1396d31f788be96e50e37189dbc7272","tid":2517610,"uid":45213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.quickmeme.com/img/6f/6ffbb4d33e6864643e5e5954869ceeb1ba258be791e800f3a92f9358428f5c7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.quickmeme.com%2Fimg%2F6f%2F6ffbb4d33e6864643e5e5954869ceeb1ba258be791e800f3a92f9358428f5c7a.jpg&h=092a6b39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47babacf8bd5b008e8b970f0e9403bd2d96236d8","tid":2517610,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b433d14e1396d31f788be96e50e37189dbc7272","tid":2517610,"uid":45213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.quickmeme.com/img/6f/6ffbb4d33e6864643e5e5954869ceeb1ba258be791e800f3a92f9358428f5c7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.quickmeme.com%2Fimg%2F6f%2F6ffbb4d33e6864643e5e5954869ceeb1ba258be791e800f3a92f9358428f5c7a.jpg&h=092a6b39&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:01:39.000Z","msg":"bam 圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}